            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/gradient-generator/">Gradient Generator</a> — Create smooth gradients from your 
              palette colors for backgrounds and visual accents.
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/color-converter/">Color Converter</a> — Convert palette colors between HEX, 
              RGB, and HSL formats for use in CSS, design tools, and code.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            All tools run in your browser with zero server uploads, so you can work with sensitive client 
            palettes without privacy concerns.
          </p>
        </section>

